WHAT IS THIS?

Object::Simple is simple,fast,useful class builder.

You can defined various type of accessors very easy way.
and prepared new method is available.

INSTALLATION

cpan Object::Simple

SAMPLES

package Book;
use Object::Simple;

sub title  : Attr { default => 'Perl' }
sub author : Attr { default => 'taro' }

